{"tid":1565072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足與家人鬧翻 無錢交學費而失學 鄺仔幫緊","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:56:23.000Z","uid":261350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"641af8a45c01b5cb33fda797f04c239372505931","tid":1565072,"uid":261350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"鄺仔fb：<br />\n<br />\n「你想繼續讀書嗎？」我問，他回話：「想，難得有入學資格。」leon（化名）是一位年輕手足，因政見不同與家人關係破裂，日前途經車站無辜被捕時亦未有伸援手。既沒有錢交學費，亦因家人不配合而未能申請學貸，因逾期未辦手續正面臨失去入學資格。「你想讀的科目是你的夢想嗎？」他苦笑：「對，期待已久。」<br />\n<br />\n我們正努力游說院校再給予入學機會，現leon僅籌措第一期學費，能否入學仍屬未知之數。「我不擔心自己，我出來分享我的故事，是想大家想一想，其他年輕人因這場運動而背負的壓力一樣很重，不少人都與最親的家人吵架，但這很不值得。」我苦笑：「知道你著緊其他手足，但現在最重要，是你能繼續讀書。」<br />\n<br />\n這場運動裡最可愛的地方，是大家怎麼都先照顧別人，回頭才照顧自己。<br />\n<br />\n今日中秋節，祝大家人月兩團圓。<br />\n<br />\n#未必會成功<br />\n#但至少盡力"},{"pid":"6f7f6ae4746c8ee0ed699ec2eb008da6a115d87e","tid":1565072,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f77b5d0cce827fb39e5c2c83cba427498fac949d","tid":1565072,"uid":261350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iktOQjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiktOQjw.jpg&h=c5fd882b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780659d1160aa18e2865be15ac23a5a1ce80815e","tid":1565072,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4e54ac92a208414f36272469d21bf8fd80e82d3","tid":1565072,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70eef12a0a7b32b72c1a42723d6fda948c46d83a","tid":1565072,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6419c90dbcf284d71b27af3cd20c03df8cae7b0","tid":1565072,"uid":283173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}